  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an unblinded, observational trial of sofosbuvir-velpatasvir in adult health care
      workers who are exposed to hepatitis C virus from needlestick injury with hollow-bore
      needles.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to assess the safety and tolerability of the use of
      sofosbuvir-velpatasvir in the setting of post-exposure prophylaxis among Health Care Workers
      exposed to HCV from needlestick injury with hollow-bore needles
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
